        {
            "title": "歐洲大型石油企業受荷莫茲海峽定價影響程度不一",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ONI_MeQ.yrRSQHgUTO0dDw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEE0B0IE_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com – 根據美國銀行的分析,歐洲最大的石油公司在<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"荷莫茲海峽\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:荷莫茲海峽;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/荷莫茲海峽\">荷莫茲海峽</a>相關的定價風險方面暴露程度不一,儘管油價上漲提振了整體現金流,但仍有少數大型石油公司面臨直接的生產風險。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該銀行強調,道達爾能源(TotalEnergies)、殼牌(<span><span>Shell</span></span> plc)、英國石油(<span><span>BP</span></span> plc)和埃尼集團(<span><span>Eni SpA</span></span>)是唯一擁有大量股權產量實際受困於荷莫茲海峽的歐洲\"大型石油\"企業。其中,道達爾能源的風險敞口最高,其年度集團產量中約有15%與受該海峽影響的流量相關。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-961ebe2c-bd29-3bfb-b01c-f2eb9a7d740a-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">然而,美國銀行指出,儘管這些產量在營運上面臨風險,但它們對整體稅後現金流的貢獻仍相對有限。這反映了這些公司投資組合的多元化特性,以及它們通過貿易和下游業務抵消中斷影響的能力。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">相比之下,與荷莫茲海峽相關的中斷所帶來的更廣泛影響正通過價格動態顯現。美國銀行估計,近期大宗商品市場的變動,包括布蘭特原油每桶上漲約15美元、歐洲天然氣價格走高以及煉油利潤率增強,可能在2026年為歐洲主要石油公司帶來超過250億美元的額外自由現金流。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">值得注意的是,挪威國家石油公司(<span><span>Equinor</span></span> ASA)成為油價上漲的最大受益者之一,該銀行估計,儘管該公司對荷莫茲海峽流量的直接風險敞口有限,但仍可能獲得超過20%的增量現金流上行空間。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這項分析正值投資者日益關注荷莫茲海峽中斷持續至2026年底的情境,在極端情況下可能推動油價突破每桶200美元。這類結果將加劇波動性,但也將強化全球多元化能源巨頭的定價能力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E5%A4%A7%E5%9E%8B%E7%9F%B3%E6%B2%B9%E4%BC%81%E6%A5%AD%E5%8F%97%E8%8D%B7%E8%8E%AB%E8%8C%B2%E6%B5%B7%E5%B3%BD%E5%AE%9A%E5%83%B9%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%A6%E4%B8%8D-202908202.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-29 04:55:19",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "霍爾木茲海峽追蹤：過去一天觀察到四艘船舶駛離波斯灣",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 隨著伊朗戰爭進入第二個月，只有少量船隻沿貼近伊朗海岸的航線穿越<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"霍爾木茲海峽\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:霍爾木茲海峽;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/霍爾木茲海峽\">霍爾木茲海峽</a>。過去一天裡，僅觀察到四艘船隻駛離波斯灣。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據彭博匯編的船舶追蹤數據，周六上午有兩艘液化石油氣運輸船和兩艘散貨船駛離波斯灣。這四艘船似乎都沿一條偏北航線航行，穿過伊朗Larak島和Qeshm島之間的狹窄水道。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這些動向顯示，相關航線可能已獲批准，表明德黑蘭正進一步收緊對這條狹窄水道的控制。伊朗議會正起草一項法案，擬對尋求安全通過霍爾木茲海峽的船隻徵收費用。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-eb829ba8-bbd7-38c3-876c-39354d059c19-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管泰國和馬來西亞均表示，已從伊朗獲得船隻通行保證，但經由霍爾木茲海峽的航運量與戰前水平相比仍是冰山一角。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/KA4CE2ho4hpRaeTk8FWGNg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/no/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/25eb0abed954cf2a53f2a3ad6bb160ce\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">電子干擾持續擾亂該地區的船舶追蹤系統。此外，船舶在高風險水域關閉自動識別系統(AIS)應答器，進一步降低了跟蹤數據的及時性和可靠性。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據Tankertrackers.com的數據，與伊朗有關聯的原油油輪仍在關閉應答器的情況下穿越霍爾木茲海峽，3月前23天的平均流量約為每日160萬桶。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在出港船隻方面，周六有兩艘駛往印度的液化石油氣運輸船離開波斯灣。此外，還有兩艘散貨船完成通行，其中一艘駛往巴基斯坦，另一艘駛往印度。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/tq85PWUYQl0lLu9pTdrdAQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/no/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/b60b6d2cc6f6de771e21b0a361b293ff\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由於船隻在高風險水域關閉信號航行，初步統計的通行數量可能偏低，隨著延遲數據到位，後續可能被上修。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">周六上午未觀察到有船隻駛入波斯灣。周五則有一艘伊朗油輪和一艘前往伊朗港口的散貨船在開啟應答器的情況下完成入港通行。它們同樣沿霍爾木茲海峽的偏北航線航行。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/tD93d28iCYsl.kdBDqQD_g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/no/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/22428d3c4e7503a0dd26a8fccc42c486\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">注：</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由於船舶在遠離霍爾木茲海峽之前可能不會發送位置信息，為識別可能駛離或進入波斯灣的船隻，覆蓋阿曼灣、阿拉伯海和紅海等更大範圍的自動定位系統信號被匯總</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">當發現潛在通行船舶後，會進一步研究信號記錄，以判斷相關航行是否真實，還是由信號欺騙所致，電子干擾可能會偽造船舶的實際位置</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">如果船舶的應答器尚未重新開啟，一些航行活動可能無法被探測到。與伊朗有關的油輪從波斯灣駛出經常不發送信號，直到約10天後經阿聯酋富查伊拉抵達馬六甲海峽。其他船舶可能也採取了類似策略，因此可能數日內都不會出現在追蹤屏幕上</p></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題HORMUZ TRACKER: Ships Exit Persian Gulf Through Iranian Corridor</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"1\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%9C%8D%E7%88%BE%E6%9C%A8%E8%8C%B2%E6%B5%B7%E5%B3%BD%E8%BF%BD%E8%B9%A4-%E9%81%8E%E5%8E%BB-%E5%A4%A9%E8%A7%80%E5%AF%9F%E5%88%B0%E5%9B%9B%E8%89%98%E8%88%B9%E8%88%B6%E9%A7%9B%E9%9B%A2%E6%B3%A2%E6%96%AF%E7%81%A3-150422239.html",
